	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Speraveram omnino ea, quae scripseram clarissimo viro d. legato tibi, charissime frater, communicanda iri, et quidem brevia illa fuerunt nec nunc copiosiora habeo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Summa omnium: evangelium Christi feliciter procedit in <placeName type="auto_name">Anglia</placeName> nec minus feliciter in <placeName type="auto_name">Scotia</placeName>; oportet enim evangelium ante iudicium praedicari ad fines usque orbis.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In Hispania quoque certum est ingentes esse motus, quorum sedandorum gratia illuc profectus est per mare non sine ingenti periculo et iactura rex <persName type="auto_name">Philippus</persName>, quippe qui eiectus dicitur in insulam quandam <placeName type="auto_name">Angliae</placeName>, unde tamen mox solverit in Hispaniam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="auto_name">Gallia</placeName> sic saevit persequtio contra fideles ut vix antea saevius.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic scripsit ad me hisce diebus d. <persName ref="p540" cert="high">Calvinus</persName>; culpa ascribitur <placeName type="auto_name">Guysianis</placeName> alioqui exosis <placeName type="auto_name">Galliae</placeName> et maxime nobilitati.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum per huiusmodi afflictiones solent grandescere ecclesiae.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominnum oremus, ut adsit et suae ecclesiae et suis bonis servis.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In Germania sunt multae contentiones, in <placeName ref="l61" cert="high">Saxonia</placeName> maxime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Philippus</persName> a multis petitur; videtur et ipse esse sacramentarius.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Princeps Hessus</persName> obtinet antiquum et nos amat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Multo melior est princeps <persName type="auto_name">elector Palatinus</persName> ille nuper electus aut creatus, quam fuerit qui decessit; speramus (quantum de homine sperare licet) non mediocria de illo.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtembergensis</placeName> inter alios vehementer nobis est adversarius; instigatur enim a <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentio</persName>.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed dabit dominus his quoque finem<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><hi>Vergil,</hi> Aeneis, 1, 199.</note>; ubique enim sunt viri boni, qui veritatem intelligunt et iuvant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="auto_name">Polonia</placeName> nunc nihil audimus; dicitur tamen celebranda nunc ibi fore comitia regni, et quo breviori esse liceat, mitto hic quaedam scripta, quae legas, ea tamen lege, ut mox remittas tuis inclusas, inprimis Iaskei literas, ad quas hisce diebus erit respondendum.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name">Hornus</persName>, d. <persName type="auto_name">Iuellus</persName>, qui convixit <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyri</persName>, d. <persName type="auto_name">Sampsonus</persName>, d. <persName type="auto_name">Sandus</persName>, d. <persName type="auto_name">Pilchinthonus Angli</persName>, qui hic <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> vixerunt et operam literis dederunt, omnes in <placeName type="auto_name">Anglia</placeName> facti dicuntur episcopi: Iuellus ipse scribit se designatum Sarisburiensem etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Boni haec consulas, oro.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valeas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Festinantissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 13. octobris 1559.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te mei omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">De <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernensibus</placeName> et Sabaudis alias;</foreign> ein gütlicher tag wirt zuͦ <placeName type="auto_name">Nüwenburg</placeName> 1. novembris.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro, fratri et compatri meo charissimo.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gen <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName> h. <persName type="auto_name">Hansen Schmiden</persName>, pfarreren zuͦ S. Martin.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
